replies.text: I already answered the questioned before, and I know this won't be the last time... The reason Tails is not in my videos is because he is not a canon character. My channel is specifically CANON characters only

replies.text: @Tamers12345 but you include plenty of non canon characters like star wars and lazy town characters....not to mention the OCs you make. It wouldn't hurt to include tails since he's been an OG since 2..just a suggestion friend. Please consider it
replies.author: tek

replies.text: @tek No, I will not consider it. He's a modern Sonic Character. If you followed my channel, you would be able to see that I do not support the existance of Modern Sonic in any way. Now if he appeared in Sonic Underground, that would be different. But as it stand he is not and he would look very out of place in my video. I feel that it would hurt the overall atmosphere
replies.author: Tamers12345

replies.text: @Tamers12345 both sonic and knuckles are "modern" characters by your logic, tails has a classic form that you can use...and you've stated in the past that you own SU no? You can add him easily.
replies.author: tek

replies.text:
Sonic and Bartleby are the protagonsits, and Knuckles first ever appearance on TV was in Sonic Underground. That's why they're in it. Tails would have absolutely zero chemistry with the rest of the Underground cast because he never met them. See the problem here? There are literally hundreds of actual Underground characters that would be added before I ever think about adding him into my video(Which I won't).
Also, I know nothing of Tails' personality. Because I'm an artist, I would have to take time for research because I would never in my life implement a character into my videos unless I know their personalities by heart. I don't have the time or care to do that.
replies.author: Tamers12345

replies.text: @Tamers12345 so you're a knuckle dragging ape, got it.
